  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Does what Madame Balinski said come true?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "巴林斯基夫人说的话应验了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "At a village fair, I decided to visit a fortune teller called Madame Balinski.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "在一次乡村集市上，我决定去拜访一个名叫巴林斯基夫人的算命人。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "I went into her tent, and she told me to sit down.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我走进她的帐篷，她让我坐下。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "After I had given her some money, she looked into a crystal ball and said, A relation of yours is coming to see you.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我给她一些钱后，她凝视着水晶球，说：“你的一位亲戚要来看你。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "She will be arriving this evening and intends to stay for a few days.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她今晚会到，打算住上几天。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "The moment you leave this tent, you will get a big surprise.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你一离开这顶帐篷，就会大吃一惊。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "A woman you know well will rush towards you.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "一个你非常熟悉的女人会向你冲过来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "She will speak to you, and then she will lead you away from this place.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她会和你说话，然后把你带离这里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "That is all.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "就这些。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "As soon as I went outside, I forgot all about Madame Balinski, because my wife hurried towards me.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我一走到外面，就把巴林斯基夫人的话全忘了，因为妻子匆匆向我走来。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "Where have you been hiding?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你躲到哪里去了？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "She asked impatiently.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她不耐烦地问。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "Your sister will be here in less than an hour, and we must be at the station to meet her.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你妹妹不到一小时就要到了，我们必须去车站接她。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "We are late already.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们已经迟了。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "As she walked away, I followed her out of the fair.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她走开时，我跟着她离开了集市。"
      }
    }
  ],
